# Dev default: point the app at the local API server (`bun dev` in wk-enhanced-api/).
# Vite runs on :5173 and the API on :3000 — genuinely cross-ORIGIN but same-SITE
# (both localhost), exactly mirroring wkenhanced.dev ↔ api.wkenhanced.dev in prod. So
# the credentialed-CORS + cookie path is exercised locally, not first in production.
# (The host-only cookie rides across localhost ports because cookies ignore the port.)
# Prod's value is baked by the Dockerfile build arg, not this file.
VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:3000
